ound-color: white; background-color: inherit\" title=\"coding\" class=\"hierarchy\"/> data-delivery.archive</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Data Archive System</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">0..1</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-item-type.html#item-type-choice\">choice</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Options: <a href=\"#opt-item.data-delivery.archive\">1 option</a><br/>Initial Value: Coding = <a href=\"CodeSystem-nasa-data-archive-cs.html\" title=\"https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs\">NASA Medical Data Archive Systems</a>#areas \"Astronaut Radiation Exposure Assessment System\"</td></tr>#xD;\n<tr><td colspan=\"6\" class=\"hierarchy\"><br/><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/formats.html#table\" title=\"Legend for this format\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"doco\" style=\"background-color: inherit\"/> Documentation for this format</a></td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Options Sets</b></p><a name=\"opt-item.overview.sponsor\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for overview.sponsor </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-mrid-sponsor-cs#srag (\"Space Radiation Analysis Group\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.overview.discipline\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for overview.discipline </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-mrid-discipline-cs#radiation (\"Radiation Health\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.spe-alert.alert-source\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for spe-alert.alert-source </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">NOAA Space Weather Prediction Center</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">NASA SRAG Real-time</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Partner Agency</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.spe-alert.severity\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for spe-alert.severity </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">S1 - Minor</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">S2 - Moderate</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">S3 - Strong</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">S4 - Severe</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">S5 - Extreme</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.protective-actions.shelter-location\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for protective-actions.shelter-location </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Service Module</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Node 1 (Unity)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Sleep Station</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Other optimized location</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.event-conclusion.crew-health-status\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for event-conclusion.crew-health-status </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">No symptoms reported</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Minor symptoms - monitoring</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Medical evaluation required</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.data-delivery.archive\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for data-delivery.archive </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs#areas (\"Astronaut Radiation Exposure Assessment System\")</li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
